Certainly! You can send a message from the parent window to an iframe using the `postMessage` API. Here's an example of how you can do it:

Let's assume you have the following setup:

1. Parent HTML page (`index.html`):

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Parent Page</title>
</head>
<body>
    <button id="sendMessageButton">Send Message to Iframe</button>
    <iframe id="myIframe" src="iframe.html" width="600" height="400" frameborder="0"></iframe>

    <script>
        // Get a reference to the iframe element
        var iframe = document.getElementById("myIframe");
        var sendMessageButton = document.getElementById("sendMessageButton");

        // Add a click event listener to the button
        sendMessageButton.addEventListener("click", function() {
            // Send a message to the iframe
            iframe.contentWindow.postMessage("Hello from parent!", "https://your-iframe-domain.com");
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

2. Iframe HTML page (`iframe.html`):

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Iframe Page</title>
</head>
<body>
    <script>
        // Add an event listener to listen for messages from the parent
        window.addEventListener("message", function(event) {
            // Check the origin of the message for security purposes
            if (event.origin === "https://your-iframe-domain.com") {
                // Handle the received message data
                console.log("Received message in iframe:", event.data);
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

In this example, when the button in the parent HTML page is clicked, it sends a message to the iframe using the `postMessage` API. The iframe, in turn, listens for messages using the `window.addEventListener("message", ...)` and processes the received message.

Make sure to replace `"https://your-iframe-domain.com"` with the actual domain of your iframe. Additionally, it's important to validate the `event.origin` property in the iframe's event listener to ensure that messages are coming from trusted sources.

